## Typography

- **Font family**: `Inter` (Google Font) — sans-serif fallback
- **Page title**: 20px/1.5rem, font-semibold, text-primary (`text-xl font-semibold`)
- **Page subtitle/description**: 14px, text-secondary (`text-sm text-muted-foreground`)
- **Card title**: 16px, font-medium (`text-base font-medium`)
- **Card subtitle/slug**: 14px, text-muted (`text-sm text-muted-foreground`)
- **Body text**: 14px (`text-sm`)
- **Small labels/badges**: 12px (`text-xs`)
- **Sidebar nav items**: 14px, font-normal (`text-sm`)
- **Tab labels**: 14px, font-medium
- **Form labels**: 14px, font-medium (`text-sm font-medium`)
- **Button text**: 14px, font-medium

## Spacing System

- **Page padding**: `px-6 py-6` (24px)
- **Card padding**: `p-4` or `p-5` (16-20px)
- **Section gap**: `space-y-6` (24px between sections)
- **Card list gap**: `space-y-0` (cards border-touching, divided by border)
- **Form field gap**: `space-y-4` (16px between fields)
- **Sidebar padding**: `px-3 py-2` per nav item
- **Content max-width**: `max-w-4xl mx-auto` (for forms/settings), full-width for lists

