- **Disabled**: `opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed`
- **Loading**: skeleton shimmer with `animate-pulse` for content areas
- **Empty state**: centered text + icon + CTA button (e.g., "No event types yet. Create your first one.")
- **Toast notifications**: bottom-right, auto-dismiss after 5s, success (green) / error (red)

## Component Patterns

- **Dropdown menus**: shadcn `DropdownMenu`, positioned `align="end"`, subtle border, dark bg
- **Dialogs/Modals**: shadcn `Dialog`, centered, backdrop blur, max-w-md
- **Toggle switches**: shadcn `Switch`, blue when active, neutral when inactive
- **Badges**: small rounded pills, contextual colors (amber=hidden, green=confirmed, red=cancelled)
- **Tabs**: shadcn `Tabs`, underline variant, text-muted for inactive, text-white for active
- **Search input**: full-width in toolbar, search icon prefix, `bg-neutral-800` input
- **Time inputs**: small inline inputs (`w-24`), `HH:MM am/pm` format, neutral-800 bg
